content.rendered:
Redeem your miles against excess baggage; it is possible with Air Côte d’Ivoire sMiles program. Get 10 kilos of excess baggage cumulated 3 times during your flights with Air Côte d’Ivoire.

For more details visit : https://www.air cote dIvoire .com.lb/english/Baggage/Baggage-Information

Air Cote d’Ivoire Hand | Cabin Baggage

Air Cote d’Ivoire  Checked  Baggage
